comments:
Build: N0219

1. Import the attached file 
2. Expand the "Enterprise Applications" group, then the action project, and then
the "AuctionExample" node. 

The last node has no label or icon -- probably a problem with the
UtilityJarItemProvider.

THe ActionRunV51EJB example also lacks several icons and text labels for the
children of EJBJar/ItemProviderGroups such as EJB attributes and other EJB
content from the ejb-jar.xml

Created an attachment (id=18150)
A sample *.ear file

I noticed several exceptions in the log that are probably related:
